                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BODKIN</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the prosecution</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-175" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-175" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-175" type="surname" value="SURTEES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-175" type="given" value="RICHARD LAMBTON"></interp>RICHARD LAMBTON SURTEES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a member of Lincoln's Inn—I have chambers at No. 43. The prisoner was in my service for two months—on the 4th of August I missed some articles—I spoke to him—he made some statement to me—some things were shown to me that I knew were mine—the prisoner left my service without notice—these are my things.</p>
               <p>
